<DIV>
It is my great pleasure in writing you this letter on behalf of myself and my colleagues. I have been mandated by my colleagues to look for a reliable and reputable foreign partner/trustee. I got to know of you from the Nigerian Export Promotion Council Foreign Exhibition. </DIV>
<DIV>
 </DIV>
<DIV>
